Retail Service Consultant - PT Mercedes-Benz Indonesia
Retail Service Consultant  -
Retail Service Consultant
Responsibilities
Job Responsibilities:To coordinate the implementation of workshop process consulting project in the dealership of Mercedes-Benz Indonesia.To provide clear guideline process for Mercedes-Benz Indonesia market.To prepare standardized required tools and guidelines for the MB authorized workshop.To provide coaching related to Workshop Operation Standard Process to Mercedes-Benz Indonesia Dealership.To set up KPI-Tool as standard measurement for successful implementation of the workshop consulting project.To provide consultation for the dealership for the implementation and to reach the KPI.To monitor, follow up and evaluate the implementation of Workshop Operational Standard. Qualification/Requirements:Education:Minimum of Bachelor Degree inMechanical/Mechattronic Engineering or Management of equivalent.Experience:Minimum of 4 years experience in after sales business and related to Workshop planning, reporting and standardizing in Automotive Industry.Specific Knowledge and Skills:Good understanding of Workshop Process and Workshop Infrastructure.Familiar with Workshop Management.Good English and Indonesian correspondence skills both written and spoken.Computer literate; MS Office (Word, Excel, and PowerPoint).Good interpersonal and communication skills.Good presentation skills.
